                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Uncertainties of line intensities; mainly",
                " statistical."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ADD-RES": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Obtained new values of the neutron binding energy for",
                " the compound systems 59Ni, 60Ni, 61Ni, 62Ni, and 64Ni",
                " as recoil-corrected gamma-ray energies of the ground",
                " state transitions in each compound nucleus.",
                "The gamma-ray spectra for neutron capture by 59Ni and",
                " 63Ni turned out to be not as strongly peaked at high",
                " energies as the gamma-ray spectra observed for neutron",
                " capture by the even-mass target nuclei in the A~40-64",
                " mass region."
              ]
            }
          ],
